  "description": "<h4>FAPO 32 Levels Damper Coilover Lowering Kit</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>For Honda Civic 8th Gen FD/FA/FG 2006-2011</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Mono-tube design provides larger capacity for oil and gas, ensuring a comfortable ride on streets.</li>\n<li>Ride height adjustable from 1 to 1.5 inches lower than factory height (up to 2.5 to 3 inches depending on vehicle chassis design).</li>\n<li>Full-threaded absorber tube for independent height adjustment.</li>\n<li>Adjustable pre-load spring tension (recommended pre-load of 7-10mm before installation).</li>\n<li>Pillow-ball top mount reduces noise while tuning and improves steering feel and response.</li>\n<li>High-tensile performance spring: &lt; 0.04% distortion after 600,000 cycles, with special surface treatment for enhanced durability.</li>\n<li>Manufactured from high-quality T-6061 billet aluminum with an anodized finish for superior strength and corrosion protection.</li>\n<li>Rubber boots included to protect dampers and keep them clean.</li>\n<li>Improves handling performance without sacrificing ride comfort.</li>\n<li>Quick and affordable way to upgrade your car's appearance.</li>\n<li>Easy installation with proper tools.</li>\n<li>Ideal for track, drift, fast-road, and daily driving.</li>\n<li>All pictured accessories included.</li>\n<li>Default 1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect, upgrade to 2 years with our Extended Warranty Program</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Fitment:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Honda Civic 8th Gen 2006-2011 (FD/FA/FG)</li>\n<li>Acura CSX 2006-2011</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Spring rate Front: 8 kg/mm (446 lbs/in)</li>\n<li>Spring rate Rear: 8 kg/mm (446 lbs/in)</li>\n<li>Adjustable damper: 32-level damper force adjustment</li>\n<li>Adjustable height: Yes</li>\n<li>Adjustable camber plate: Yes (front coilovers with camber plates)</li>\n<li>Colors: Red, Silvery, Black</li>\n<li>Condition: 100% Brand New</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Package Includes:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>1 set of coilover spring kit (2 front + 2 rear)</li>\n<li>1 pair of wrenches for height adjustment</li>\n<li>4 waving rings</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Shipping Policy:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>We ship everything within 2 business days from receiving payment.</li>\n<li>Faster shipping options are available.</li>\n<li>Every package is insured for damages or loss. Please report any issues within 24 hours of delivery.</li>\n<li>Damage/loss claims will take up to 10 days to process through UPS, FedEx, or USPS.</li>\n<li>Packages over $500 will require a signature upon delivery to ensure package value.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Warranty:</h4>\n<p>All items carry a standard 1-year warranty from the date of purchase. Proof of purchase (order number) is required. To expedite any warranty claim, please provide clear photos and detailed descriptions. In most cases, the defective item does not need to be returned. Additional information may be requested to accurately diagnose and resolve the issue.</p>\n<h4>Important Notice:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Any returned item(s) without a Return Authorization number will be rejected.</li>\n<li>Please return items in their original packaging and ensure all packages are securely wrapped.</li>\n<li>If you wish to cancel an order before it is dispatched, please contact us by message as quickly as possible.</li>\n</ul>",
